<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_2bdd54f4-5de2-4d33-b725-cfa36aa3a618" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S34C2</sptc><title id="_f7f44022-706c-474b-8308-10a1982b977e">Reference building</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_829ba886-57af-41e5-817c-acdcc3843be2" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f0dfde94-a40d-4214-a47b-72d88f940436">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1188_1.0.0.xml#_eea4a10f-c51b-47b3-ab0b-72043e96d6c8" id="_4ab8ba92-d1b4-42f8-aa24-f53bfe4e249c" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">annual greenhouse gas emissions</xref> must be calculated for the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1424_4.10.0.xml#_5dfc40fe-dad0-46ab-9923-f7643beb2160" id="_bcd42f88-cb8a-4050-ab3e-bf41c3b272ea" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">reference building</xref> in accordance with the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_91d2c6d4-ef51-4bf1-a800-8daf67372a5b">The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1424_4.10.0.xml#_5dfc40fe-dad0-46ab-9923-f7643beb2160" id="_a38c6a43-fbe9-4756-b6de-8b0a0bba1f80" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">reference building</xref> must—<ol><li>subject to (b), (c) and (d), comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_492328d0-25fe-407e-8006-079efbc8ac8c" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/132_0.36.0.xml#_47a76707-fe78-450a-a2d9-3ef9b47f81bb" id="_8dab270d-cf2b-408a-a67b-8505b7fb341c" scope="local" type="part">Parts J4</xref> to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/143_0.30.0.xml#_f95314cf-e059-4981-9bd2-a4662a26a949" id="_bdb2a650-3ab9-42bf-87e8-45bb8df300fd" scope="local" type="part">J8</xref>; and</li><li>have the minimum amount of mechanical ventilation <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_0d34b13a-c6e9-42f6-ba5f-be86fde3841e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/57_0.9.0.xml#_a2a7a658-2b2e-4234-bc6b-f424abbfba1c" id="_695e52d5-93c5-4655-84e9-f18b1681c0ed" scope="local" type="part">Part F6</xref>; and</li><li>be provided with a solar photovoltaic system that complies with—<ol><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6194_0.27.0.xml#_9edff9ca-9adf-4366-b1fc-5a8895744b02" id="_273e8fea-c710-4501-b19c-8b777412a96a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J9D5(2)(a)</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6194_0.27.0.xml#_d4d49e63-05e6-4ddf-b334-f78575e1fe01" id="_328132be-1a06-4cf7-89e6-e3bcd595b43f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J9D5(3)</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6194_0.27.0.xml#_63aaf1cf-b105-4bd5-8c0a-d238f1343637" id="_cd173831-584a-4ba8-a7a5-5f289f845206" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J9D5(4)</xref> with PV panels modelled as parallel to the roof and assuming an average solar photovoltaic panel power rating of 225 W/m<sup id="_7ccd009b-128d-4891-a3b5-b1dd48f58a8a">2</sup>; or</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6194_0.27.0.xml#_9edff9ca-9adf-4366-b1fc-5a8895744b02" id="_13ee9bb9-eca9-49a9-a39a-6665e8470396" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J9D5(2)(b)</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6194_0.27.0.xml#_d4d49e63-05e6-4ddf-b334-f78575e1fe01" id="_2f4eace3-a666-432f-ada7-bc8dd73178f1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J9D5(3)</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6194_0.27.0.xml#_63aaf1cf-b105-4bd5-8c0a-d238f1343637" id="_f9d13c98-0f7a-4cde-b472-18a597d4cc8a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J9D5(4)</xref>.</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_a2708232-be58-4c74-bb5b-c2fcc989f6a5">The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_2206dff9-68dd-4f26-b170-402cba8413eb" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external walls</xref> must have a solar absorptance of 0.6.</li><li id="_c54f5a4d-b437-4d0d-8ec6-bfcfca988481">The U-Value of the wall-glazing construction must be calculated according to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/206_0.12.0.xml#_9d1943e6-4031-4b09-8bf3-507e93497fea" id="_949b7ca8-dd3d-4bff-8582-842ebc666297" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">S37C3</xref>.</li><li id="_a3378295-4025-46e9-a8e8-b1a9d19e040b">The solar admittance of the wall-glazing construction must be calculated according to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/206_0.12.0.xml#_9d1943e6-4031-4b09-8bf3-507e93497fea" id="_802ebc79-06ed-49f4-a3c1-4dba4bea4b53" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">S37C5</xref>.</li><li id="_13a7aec4-9555-48ea-8532-c5c475c27144">Where <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/7892_0.4.0.xml#_f39765e3-60bd-4ca0-885e-5556fdf9d56e" id="_24997919-47d6-47bc-8e8c-0d4c7d782599" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">J1V3(1)(b)(i)</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3372_3.23.0.xml#_96c5d91c-f777-41e6-b560-7d2ca07e87ee" id="_f50b6d89-a27e-4e55-ac18-aedd2a51e5bd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">J1V3(1)(b)(ii)</xref> applies, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_e6d2a734-3a24-4814-bda8-0535afbeb3ed" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> must—<ol><li>for 95% of the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_af748c8c-d8a0-46e7-9a68-f875afa9e68a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref>, achieve dry bulb temperatures between—<ol><li>18°C to 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_9132b685-242a-41ee-8803-a9240534315c" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy; and</li><li>subject to (ii), 21°C to 24°C in all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_3d756cf4-2b51-45e1-8da7-9ce0e29ef982" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li>if the proposed building has no mechanically provided cooling or has mixed mode cooling, have the same method of control and control set points for non-mechanical cooling as the proposed building.</li></ol></li><li id="_6336eefd-1126-4b44-9d9b-a11e417c15e8">The infiltration rate in each zone must be—<ol><li>0.7 air changes per hour throughout all zones when there is no mechanically supplied <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1388_0.4.0.xml#_eb74131f-b9dc-42bf-89c2-f68b788f9636" id="_66d1de5c-e31b-4859-9322-401955497e18" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">outdoor air</xref>; and</li><li>0.35 air changes per hour throughout all zones at all other times.</li></ol></li><li id="_68da6af2-a397-4a9c-9b98-aeb2a4abf199">The artificial lighting must achieve the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_001a8085-cffe-4ca9-9ad1-d73b12b5e67a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> maximum <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1347_2.2.0.xml#_cb831616-4067-469f-ae62-121c80dd2c31" id="_1416756b-b4b5-494c-8daa-3e65bf265856" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">illumination power density</xref> in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/140_0.26.0.xml#_e4bad8ff-4479-4285-a091-145ca2e85197" id="_0a2ff6c0-54ea-4c44-b2ec-24690ad75e26" scope="local" type="part">Part J7</xref> without applying the control device adjustment factors.</li><li id="_138c3f97-ba58-4b41-8534-44f0145eb1fd"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1371_0.4.0.xml#_6d2d2ec4-793d-4384-98a5-f39ff765e8c8" id="_a3817d0f-a60c-46c2-aa31-72ac8f6fc04c" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Minimum Energy Performance Standards</xref> must be applied to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_1af924c3-c7da-4f38-abc7-4751acb0399f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref> not covered by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/138_0.29.0.xml#_05bbc3db-9aa4-4fd6-b2a2-0a5551074b52" id="_3b643ed4-60cc-42e6-a0d3-038572547c10" scope="local" type="part">Parts J6</xref> to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/143_0.30.0.xml#_f95314cf-e059-4981-9bd2-a4662a26a949" id="_fbe4c40c-b42c-4ef9-9bec-32bd91e8d85c" scope="local" type="part">J8</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>